name: Angkringan Vibes
description:
you know! in my country, for a hangout place other than a cafe is "Angkringan". a place with a simple setup and very cheap prices. Angkringan is an option to gather while eating and drinking at low prices. 
Food starts at a thousand and no more than 10 thousand. usually just covered with a tent and on the side of the road. but that's the atmosphere that makes angkringan has its own charm. if you go to Indonesia, and happen to be in the Yogyakarta area. 
Please try! :)
